01:28:49,015 --> 01:28:51,344
Vamos a caminar.

1287
01:28:51,597 --> 01:28:57,375
Ven, chico. A ser si te podemos
conseguir tu gallina asada.

1288
01:29:00,070 --> 01:29:01,373
